&lt;p&gt;A 60-minute discussion space for faculty.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Do you grapple with leverage reading assignments in your course? Are you curious how you might engage students with course readings? Are you wondering how AI is impacting reading practices?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
